  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Construction Site Engineer (LTA Projects)<br /><strong>Company:</strong> DONG CONSTRUCTION & ENGINEERING PTE LTD<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore</p><h3>Role Overview</h3><p>DONG CONSTRUCTION & ENGINEERING PTE LTD is hiring a Construction Site Engineer to support ongoing LTA infrastructure projects. This role is hands-on and site-based, driving execution quality, coordination, and delivery performance.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Manage day-to-day site operations to ensure works are delivered safely, on schedule, and to specification.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with LTA, consultants, subcontractors, and internal teams on construction methodology, sequencing, and site constraints.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and review method statements, work procedures, and risk assessments in accordance with project requirements.</p></li><li><p>Oversee site supervision, quality control, and inspection processes; ensure rectifications are closed out promptly.</p></li><li><p>Monitor progress and resources (manpower, plant, materials) and support reporting on productivity and performance.</p></li><li><p>Support submissions, site records, and documentation (e.g., daily reports, inspection records, as-built updates).</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with relevant regulations, safety standards, and project quality requirements.</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>3 years of construction site engineering experience</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Proven experience working on <strong>LTA projects</strong> in Singapore (mandatory).</p></li><li><p>Diploma/Degree in Civil Engineering or relevant discipline.</p></li><li><p>Strong coordination capability across multiple stakeholders; able to drive site execution decisively.</p></li><li><p>Familiar with local construction practices, quality requirements, and site safety compliance.</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Opportunity to work on major LTA infrastructure projects.</p></li><li><p>Performance-driven environment with growth opportunities.</p></li></ul><h3>How to Apply</h3><p>Interested candidates, please submit your CV to <a href=\"mailto:careers@dongce.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">careers@dongce.com.sg</a> with the email subject: <strong>“Application – Construction Site Engineer (LTA)”</strong>.</p>",
